             sworn. - Messrs. Morley, Rowe, Old, and Boddington, are <rs id="t17971206-40-viclabel222" type="occupation">partners in shipping</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971206-40-victim404 t17971206-40-viclabel222"></join>
